   • non-binary A → a0/a1 two-level contrast (factor/{1,2}/{-1,1}); >2 levels is an
     ERROR not a silent subset (would shift the C-averaging population → wrong estimand).
   • coverage → inst/sim/gauge_coverage.R, closed-form truth W=tau*aM/(bA+(bM+tau)*aM).
     ANALYTIC half VALIDATED locally (nsim=1000, MCSE~0.01, inst/sim/results/
     analytic_coverage_nsim1000.csv): W-CI coverage 0.855-0.887 near null, FLAT across
