📋 DESCRIPTION
Compute P_med, a scale-free probabilistic effect size
for causal mediation analysis. Provides interpretable
measures of mediation strength.

Version: 0.2.0 (GitHub release 2026-06-11, non-CRAN; pins medfit@v0.3.0)
  — adds method="mbco" + parallel (joint) P_med
  — 2026-06-14: dev→main release PR #4 merged; main was stale (v0.1.0/v0.2.0
